publisher			Royal Polygon							
publish_time	 2015年10月29日		
desc_long							评测						“... vagueness and ambiguity are their own virtues in Sun Dogs.”Kill Screen“... an engaging, thought provoking exploration of how humans might use technology to transform ourselves and our solar system.”Game Jolt“... a memorable and intelligent flavour to its economically written stories.”FailBetter Games												关于这款游戏							Sun Dogs is about exploring our inner solar system, altering your body, and embracing death. In a future where humanity alters itself without a second thought, you must do the same. Skim along the Sun's corona, float in the Venusian clouds, travel the Martian plains.When your body dies, your mind will be given a new one, and you will keep going.FeaturingExpansive and unique science fiction, across planets, moons, and space stationsDynamic text reacts to your character and actions Full modding system allowing additions or rewrites to the entire game						
